  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nI am trying to connect a Besu node with a Remix smart contract, making use of the Web3 Provider of Remix. I am following an [example ](https://besu.hyperledger.org/en/stable/HowTo/Get-Started/Starting-node/) provided in the Hyperledger Besu official website, but I am not able to make the connection. \r\n\r\nI am making use of an AWS EC2 ubuntu instance and Docker. The docker compose file can be found attached, together with an screenshot proving that I am actually allowing AWS to listen on port 8545 and 8546, which correspond to RPC-HTTP and WebSocket connections.\r\n\r\nWhen trying to connect to the port 8545 (I attach an screenshot of how I am doing so on Remix), I get an error message which I also attach below. I am checking the logs of the Besu container, but I don't get to see any actual logs corresponding to this connection. I am also attaching a screenshot of the starting logs of Besu, in which it can be seen that Besu is actually listen for RPC-HTTP connections on the port 8545.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce (Bug)\r\n1. I am first running the docker-compose.yaml file on the VM machine in VSCode, making use of a Remote SSH connection to AWS.\r\n2. Afterwards I go to remix, and I try to connect with the Besu node\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior:** [What you expect to happen]\r\n\r\nThe expected behavior is that Remix would connect to the Besu node on port 8545.\r\n\r\n**Actual behavior:** [What actually happens]\r\n\r\nThe actual behavior is that Remix is not able to connect to the Besu node, and I get no logs on the Besu docker container.\r\n\r\n**Frequency:** [What percentage of the time does it occur?]\r\n\r\nIt happens all the time. I haven't been able to make the connection even once.\r\n\r\n### Versions (Add all that apply)\r\n* Software version:  Version 3\r\n* OS Name & Version:  Windows 10\r\n* Virtual Machine software & version: Ubuntu 18.04\r\n* Docker Version: latest\r\n* Cloud VM, type, size: AWS EC2 t2.medium instance.\r\n\r\n\r\n![Ports AWS](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/78016113/115996485-bc472000-a5df-11eb-84b5-95969ce1cfb2.PNG)\r\n![Remix](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/78016113/115996488-bc472000-a5df-11eb-9233-202707585d5a.PNG)\r\n![Remix_Error](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/78016113/115996490-bcdfb680-a5df-11eb-9cc4-abd9e6e27e2e.PNG)\r\n![Besu container](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/78016113/115996491-bd784d00-a5df-11eb-85b8-95a31a1e2951.PNG)\r\n![BesuStartingLogs](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/78016113/115996492-bd784d00-a5df-11eb-9350-b3c338e1a623.PNG)\r\n\r\n\r\n",
